Class DB2400Dialect

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ConversionContext
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DB2400V7R3Dialect
    public class DB2400Dialect
extends DB2Dialect
    An SQL dialect for DB2/400. This class provides support for DB2 Universal Database for iSeries, also known as DB2/400.
